query:
SELECT r.id, r.status, r.started_at, r.finished_at, r.error_message,
       l.level, l.message, l.created_at
FROM execution_runs r
LEFT JOIN execution_logs l ON l.run_id = r.id
ORDER BY r.id DESC, l.created_at ASC
LIMIT 50;
